HEADWORD: Zeus
<hw>Zeus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Gr. Myth.)</fld>
<def>The chief deity of the Greeks, and ruler of the upper world (cf.
<er>Hades</er>). He was identified with <xex>Jupiter</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

